---
title: Smoky Sweet Potato Pita Pockets with Golden Raisins & Shaved Vegetable Salad
description: The sweet-and-smoky combination of roasted sweet potato, golden raisins, and earthy cumin makes for a killer pita filling. A little creamy hummus holds all that deliciousness in place. We've rounded out the plate with a crisp and refreshing shaved vegetable salad to boot. Bon appetit!
